  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE NEW SECTION 89-8-47, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CREATE THE CRIME OF \"FRAUDULENT UTILITY CONVERSION\"; TO PROVIDE PENALTIES FOR THE CRIME; TO AMEND SECTION 89-8-23, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO ADD UTILITY PAYMENTS AS A DUTY OF THE LANDLORD; TO BRING FORWARD SECTION 89-8-25, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH PROVIDES DUTIES OF TENANTS, FOR PURPOSES OF AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
